title: GIANT 4Br+ LIVE WORK
posting_body: ['GIANT LIVE WORK 4Br+ in SOMA', 'This place is super spacious in the heart of SOMA.', 'Blocks away from Safeway, Wholefoods etc. walking distance to the Giants Stadium and the Embarcadero waterfront.', 'Large bi-level live/work loft in modern building on Brannan Street.', 'Close to Caltrain, 7 minute walk.', "Safeway, Walgreens, Trader Joe's and Whole Foods within 2 to 4 blocks.", 'Within proximity to Financial District, Embarcadero and Union Square.', 'Easy freeway access for 280, 101 & 80E.', '3D Virtual', 'https://kuula.co/share/NnmfX/collection/7vMbl?logo=0&info=0&fs=1&vr=1&sd=1&initload=0&thumbs=1', 'Features:', '- Available now', '- Modern live/work building', '- Top floor, corner unit', '- Spacious, airy loft with large, expansive windows', '- North & West facing, plenty of natural light', '- High ceilings', '- Skylight', '- Broad living area and separate dining area', '- 4 fully enclosed bedrooms (2 upstairs, 2 downstairs)', '- Walk-in closet on mezzanine level', '- 2 full bathrooms', '- Gas fireplace', '- Custom center island', '- Modern kitchen with maple cabinetry, black granite countertops, stainless steel refrigerator, stove, dishwasher and garbage disposal', '- Laundry facility in building', '- 1 parking, additional', '- Pet policy: under 25 lbs & breed restriction.', 'Additional monthly assessment for dog', '- Elevator', 'Virtual Tour', 'https://kuula.co/share/collection/7vMbl?logo=0&info=0&fs=1&vr=1&sd=1&initload=0&thumbs=1']
